### Abstract ###

Name: 		mate-doc-utils
Version: 	1.4.0
Release: 	2%{?dist}
License: 	GPLv2+ and LGPLv2+ and GFDL
Group: 		Development/Tools
Summary: 	Documentation utilities for MATE
URL: 		http://pub.mate-desktop.org
Source: 	http://pub.mate-desktop.org/releases/1.4/%{name}-%{version}.tar.xz

BuildArch: noarch

